Leke Baiyewu, Abuja A member of the House of Representatives, Yusuf Kila, is dead. Until his death on Thursday, he was Chairman of the Committee on Customs and Excise. A top official in the House confirmed the death to our correspondent. The message to our correspondent read, “May Allah grant Rep. Yusuf Kila Aljanah (Chairman Customs). House of Representatives. Age: 70yrs. Party: All Progressive Congress (APC). State: Jigawa. We just lost him.” The House Committee on Customs and Excise, which was grilling the Controller General of the Nigeria Customs Service, Col. Hameed Ali (retd.), had to adjourn abruptly when the news filtered in. Details later…